data.description: Enjoy summer in this adorable Rotterdam home in the Mohonasen school district! Featuring 2 first floor bedrooms, 1st floor tiled full bath, open tiled kitchen with stainless appliances that leads to a large dining area that includes room for a home office. Great location, conveniently located near major highways and walk to restaurants, shopping, parks and grocery. Other features: Detached 2 car garage, deck and nice backyard that has fencing, lots of off street parking, step up attic great for storage and partially finished basement with bar area. Call to schedule your private showing today!!
